name: SPECIAL EDITION: PUNKEYBOY
description:
PUNKEY is a rebellious boy, he decided to join our gang because he was fed up with human society and its rules. He allowed us to experiment with his body to turn him into a unique boy, but in the process he has lost his eyesight. His lack of vision was not a hindrance to gain the respect of everyone and achieve feats that made him quickly rise to the top of our gang. 
Today he holds the position of PUNKBOY$ division commander. This boy is one of 2KEY's favorites.

> Special Gift Edition | Wednesday, October 13, 2021.
